<TEXT>
Bombay police said two men were arrested yesterday for planting bombs in a
wave of attacks which killed at least 250 people and injured more than 1,200
in Bombay last week, writes Shiraz Sidhva in New Delhi.
Bombay police chief Amarjeet Singh Samra said one of the men had driven a
