smugglers who have since escaped to Dubai.
The police allege that the Memons have been involved in the narcotics trade,
gun-running, silver smuggling and foreign exchange rackets.
Police said the intention of the bombings was to 'disturb the peace in
Bombay and take advantage of the turmoil to further their illegal business.'
Meanwhile, the death toll in the blast in central Calcutta rose to 80.
Police have found no links between the Bombay and Calcutta blasts.
