               Estimates for year ending March 1993 (Ybn)
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
                   REVENUE        PRE-TAX PROFIT        NET PROFIT
                1993    1992      1993      1992      1993      1992
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
Nomura           345   421.7         0      44.1         2      31.6
Daiwa            240   321.1        -8       9.3       -10     -43.5
Nikko            230   287.9         0       3.1       -11     -25.9
Yamaichi         185   231.4       -39     -36.5       -48     -53.2
